---
---
<button class="hamburger-btn" id="hamburgerBtn" aria-label="菜单">
  <i class="fas fa-bars"></i>
</button>

<div class="app-container" id="appContainer">
  <aside class="sidebar" id="sidebar">
    <div class="sidebar-title">CLRA</div>
    <button class="sidebar-btn" id="refreshBtn"><i class="fas fa-sync-alt"></i> 刷新</button>
    <button class="sidebar-btn" id="settingsBtn"><i class="fas fa-cog"></i> 设置</button>
    <button class="sidebar-btn" id="aboutBtn"><i class="fas fa-info-circle"></i> 关于</button>
    <div class="sidebar-spacer"></div>
    <div class="sidebar-footer">工具列表</div>
  </aside>

  <main class="main-content">
    <header class="top-header">
      <div class="header-text">
        <h1><i class="fas fa-tools"></i> CLRA 工具分发平台</h1>
        <p>抓牢学生机房学习主权，发现并下载优质工具</p>
      </div>
      <a class="client-dl-btn" href="./client" aria-label="下载桌面客户端">
        <i class="fas fa-download"></i> 下载客户端
      </a>
    </header>

    <div class="loading" id="loading">
      <div class="spinner"></div>
      <p>正在加载工具列表…</p>
    </div>

    <div class="error-msg" id="errorMsg">
      <i class="fas fa-exclamation-triangle"></i>
      <h3>加载失败</h3>
      <p>无法加载工具列表，请检查网络或联系管理员</p>
      <div class="cors-info">
        <h4><i class="fas fa-info-circle"></i> 常见原因</h4>
        <ul>
          <li><strong>跨域请求被阻止</strong> – 服务器需配置 CORS</li>
          <li><strong>网络连接失败</strong> – 检查域名可达性</li>
          <li><strong>清单文件缺失</strong> – 确认存在 clra_manifest.json 或 jfkl_manifest.json</li>
          <li><strong>泛域名解析失败</strong> – 检查域名格式</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="empty-state" id="emptyState">
      <i class="fas fa-box-open"></i>
      <h3>没有找到工具</h3>
      <p>当前没有可用的工具，请稍后刷新或联系管理员添加新的工具源。</p>
      <button class="empty-btn" onclick="document.getElementById('refreshBtn').click()">
        <i class="fas fa-sync-alt"></i> 刷新
      </button>
    </div>

    <div class="tools-grid" id="toolsGrid"></div>

    <footer>
      <p>&copy; 2026 CLRA 工具分发平台</p>
    </footer>
  </main>
</div>

<!-- 设置面板 -->
<div class="settings-panel" id="settingsPanel">
  <div class="panel-head">
    <span><i class="fas fa-sliders"></i> 设置</span>
    <button class="panel-close" id="panelClose"><i class="fas fa-times"></i></button>
  </div>
  <div class="setting-section">
    <div class="section-head">外观</div>
    <div class="setting-row">
      <label><i class="fas fa-palette"></i> 主题</label>
      <div class="setting-control">
        <button class="btn-sm" id="themeBtn">
          <i class="fas fa-moon" id="themeIcon"></i>
          <span id="themeLabel">浅色</span>
        </button>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="setting-row">
      <label><i class="fas fa-eyedropper"></i> 强调色</label>
      <div class="setting-control">
        <input type="color" id="accentColorPicker" class="color-input" value="#0078D4" />
        <span style="font-size:13px;">点击选择颜色</span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="cache-section">
    <div class="cache-head">缓存状态</div>
    <div class="setting-row" id="cacheStatusRow">
      <span><i class="fas fa-database"></i> 加载中…</span>
    </div>
    <div class="setting-row" id="cacheDetailRow">
      <span>最后同步: --</span>
    </div>
    <div class="setting-row" id="toolCountRow">
      <span>工具数量: --</span>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="debug-section">
    <div class="debug-head">调试日志</div>
    <div class="debug-log" id="debugLog"></div>
  </div>
</div>

<!-- 关于弹窗 -->
<div class="modal-overlay" id="aboutModal">
  <div class="modal-content">
    <h2>CLRA 工具分发平台（网页版）</h2>
    <p class="modal-version">版本: 1.0.0</p>
    <p class="modal-author">作者: 星影 (XingYing) &amp; CLRA Team</p>
    <p class="modal-group">技术讨论群: 1071829146</p>
    <p class="modal-group">加入审核群: 1073170610</p>
    <p class="modal-desc">计算机实验室反抗联盟工具箱 - 基于 Web 的工具分发平台</p>
    <div class="modal-license">
      <p>本项目为开源项目，源代码托管在 <a href="https://github.com/CLRA-org/dra" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">GitHub</a>，采用 Apache License 2.0 许可。</p>
    </div>
    <button class="modal-close-btn" id="closeAboutBtn">关闭</button>
  </div>
</div>

<!-- Cookie 横幅 -->
<div id="cookieBanner" class="cookie-banner hidden">
  <p>本网站使用 Cookie 及 Microsoft Clarity 进行匿名分析，以改善用户体验。继续使用即表示您同意我们使用这些技术。</p>
  <button id="cookieAccept">接受</button>
  <button id="cookieReject" class="cookie-reject">拒绝</button>
</div>
